column5:
Review submited to special volume 'High Solid Dispersions' ed. M.
  Cloitre, Vol. xx of 'Advances and Polymer Science' (Springer, Berlin, 2009);
  some figures slightly cut

11 pages, 6 Postscript figures; requires asp2006.sty; as published,
  except with updated references; for a version with full resolution figures,
  see http://chandra.as.utexas.edu/~kormendy/kormendy-rome.pdf

no figure, we gave a proof of the conjecture in the second version;
  we modified section 4.2 of the first version to correct an error in
  Proposition 4.4 and give more general result
